	)
	(text "Atmega Hardware Design Considerations p7,p8 -> 10kR and 330R for switch. The 100nF capacitor is not used for Arduino (Produces errors with DTR)\nThe 100nF capacitor on DTR (CP2102) is used for tricking the Atmega into Bootloader mode\n\n\n"
