	(text "If USB is present and no external input voltage. The USB will power the ATMEGA\nIf USB is present and there is external input voltage. The external voltage will power the ATMEGA\nIf USB is not present and there is external input voltage. The external voltage will power the ATMEGA. The 3.3V output won't work"
