	)
	(text "XC6206 Torex Datasheet p1 -> 1uF ceramic capacitor on input and output. 7V Maximum operating Voltage\nXC6206 UWM Datasheet p2 -> 1uF ceramic capacitor on the input and output. 9V Maximum operating Voltage"
